" alt="Supporters hold a poster of Ekrem Imamoglu during a rally in Ankara in 2025. Photographer: Serdar Ozsoy&amp;amp;#x2F;Getty Images" width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="2025 年安卡拉集会上，支持者举着埃克雷姆·伊玛莫格鲁的海报。摄影师：Serdar Ozsoy&amp;amp;#x2F;Getty Images" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/in.Ll.DU1QvA/v0/-1x-1.jpg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 4px;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4;"&gt; 2025 年安卡拉的一次集会上，支持者举着伊玛莫鲁的海报。&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4; font-style: italic;"&gt;摄影师：Serdar Ozsoy/Getty Images&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴内斯&lt;/strong&gt;驳回了削减移民或加强边境检查的想法，尽管民意调查显示该国极右翼一国党的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=8170323126524fdda82c97d70887dddf&amp;amp;_e=Qpo8Vp2sdQAn38cUFysLch5YsET8p4OMjneC2ov30hWNxZsNVSp2hnU_XVBwuM8VNzNym_-wy6taXmKdF8UIY0cUAXmQ-5bz4692vMJGGgcHjwSVPywLMNUfvBOlZq2GU1ZmrcXZlGlLYuuGkZegsK6wIfPBCB9MHPlIepmVDpxsDCXhreT1VGsEZcuRKEcBLnRFv-yGdSDEAJ_wSMCMHMmGTEQ8cyYZjCJOmBuF18ph6GOX0vPyWl8rvm9lUkLRsO8NR8bUc5e5dXIoeueN8WqxRML1Ly6wOxdb7uN2vtVK7WstB0VXW7MQt2h57zKVNR7G74mH2x3_uFQ-Ql7VqVgI0e4eerYxC_kbeoml1yU5u6DVk_X6BBBRBb6F1QQPhdFgRQxcHnWRRAVYITjfGHuTnAjpHlgjCqnj0ZxQW2ApGmzbG2blkQpFkiSx65X3ZMb5yi7woJum5Jj70JnF9vwGw5Xv0_EVKoFqZUogDgo%3D" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="随着极右翼势力的壮大，澳大利亚阿尔巴尼人拒绝削减移民"&gt;支持率激增&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=8170323126524fdda82c97d70887dddf&amp;amp;_e=Qpo8Vp2sdQAn38cUFysLch5YsET8p4OMjneC2ov30hXQ6bBI6joGRRhckjnpLut45a8IJydgDnNqH2zQjCl0ivjYaV81wuQiUqbx09IESpqL74UzwdvEuhAJGu12a2-5djEIfyndpHwn2BiVOLqtB1b--hC_GOk_AHuzplAlvS0TzQOVfEZa_BGJ1YNh2VBauA9JppPanM7PKOn6zf0ohFV78c1lI8Rx6tMbxt209QTIWSo5Chayz_DCkZPp8cYPcjvOfLI05cDP1TruwZbh-Q%3D%3D" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;订阅华盛顿版时事通讯，&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;了解来自美国首都的新闻，并在美国东部时间工作日下午 1 点和 5 点观看彭博电视台的《权力平衡》节目。&lt;/em&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;每日图表&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;figure style="margin: 20px 0;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iJOBCdwv4Ws0/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" alt="" width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="替代" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iJOBCdwv4Ws0/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 4px;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;早在李总统帮助韩国综合股价指数成为世界上最热门的股指之前，他就曾是一名 30 多岁的日内交易员，苦苦挣扎。消息人士称，几十年后，他仍然感到恼火，因为控股股东以牺牲普通投资者的利益为代价而削减交易，从而扩大了他的损失。这促使他在 6 月上台后实施了全面改革，引发&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=8170323126524fdda82c97d70887dddf&amp;amp;_e=Qpo8Vp2sdQAn38cUFysLch5YsET8p4OMjneC2ov30hWNxZsNVSp2hnU_XVBwuM8V526dWljaHIqJdN16OrI83woBYIvW-lvurR4ytOb-vm5nqJDVBnpPVGwndEA3fCNSAaIJoJ2Zuyc-Qvm6YZQyRiESIH9fi-pBNEpW5GlMNeOTn3lBePVwYAe7smKv-kQ4rE5iXm-Ndgs5qBpMZxycqWCPIg2sYU3ZYln2CqpIaOynGxODAvs_frbQ3DSv5pYNwDe_fOhUL_PdjOgWAulRa9nepESCrf-DF4kwIhJ9oaetHOveUjuI0orlGrYgUx2IospCntJS4P5JYkHTZC2tX7muw-6fjQB-FaBVrWaxlMMOVDG4F3mszMs68Fw2e_lGRVDYHz9oGFggB9e1_1eN9_Gq1ssTCM4hj-vMVgSVkqqmfoL-30TiFa7BwXrJphstzXhLRvNYzW5PPe2pqvLhYsYrldlftDmV77HR2yu3JD8%3D" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="韩国总统如何将其市场打造成世界上表现最好的市场"&gt;了股市的强劲反弹&lt;/a&gt;，甚至超过了他的“Kospi 5,000”竞选口号。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;最后&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;参观格陵兰岛的兴趣&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=8170323126524fdda82c97d70887dddf&amp;amp;_e=Qpo8Vp2sdQAn38cUFysLch5YsET8p4OMjneC2ov30hWNxZsNVSp2hnU_XVBwuM8VHJcdCa7qFyz4CtMAEotK7UNCC1yZ-PAZ4NjUhhgS-t5FurnoxG3ILJ-Fql7mkzgMNi_mA7lYafasstDXIEYWruSDQLw2kef7ZDQu6zVTGYMgKm-nrjitWYCw0OfHU3DST9LaOdLKte_mRhHMkTmsb0RC1sY4-z-1SWUTLHRn79DU94Zdkk8WztFyvn9mj5CnjbOUDgwRge-yL4RhJegFqM0AKp5N1NA8yLRujzq--ltRO33NJNXnLGRiXbw7_9Za89_d7qBHujM5ik9SoBg3vJ34vxhroww4p0132vuMZ_A1ADzo8qATQHzEJ4N7aes_cIUtKYlHuJYGLmQ58LtsblVk_EbYdRvQkEPqyYTpkAjICkOP6gKaqu_KgiaNNYU-TT8L13YPsleywWa-xK2WCHQWOuUB1GjIR3F6dk2jppg%3D" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="随着特朗普收购威胁的减弱，格陵兰岛重新关注旅游业"&gt;从未如此高涨&lt;/a&gt;，到 2025 年，前往这片丹麦北极领土的国际游客数量将是前一年的两倍。随着&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=8170323126524fdda82c97d70887dddf&amp;amp;_e=Qpo8Vp2sdQAn38cUFysLch5YsET8p4OMjneC2ov30hWNxZsNVSp2hnU_XVBwuM8V3Wp-jexLHFMZ-FGNf4QMm1ea6B7hReThk18JnwTBcVawUXiTlqhmhawNPFYvuRXjQecJDfHsQPuUXg2JBg8VteZ1dZI6nHKVLNjDszBu3wygSbMy1ddfycBr4eWnSnAnE0V4-f4skd4Y6mOzGCrvt04bOieLpTwl-xlKc45ECvJoaJxvvssHW5DyiRHWCV0O2d7JPxx4o1Gnw_Tq_0C4v-Epgvg0zGytEZmkbfYlO_x6DDgAjbopy6YykZ36th8i4C0hedTSW9D7jpiTuSSPYczQZ_jeu5WpJcsB6PkMOFUWKoUV1yUEN1asN7KEVoYDBnvq2O-56LCOcdkjlk1cqZUUPJnaaL5Fm857iHeY_I3m8cdR5PDJ7aClG2Ilv7BIVI0_6wYHscP7Em33BlfA56n3xxIQPc1tkodtEQHb3pM%3D" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="特朗普为何想要格陵兰岛？他真的能抓住吗？"&gt;特朗普在岛上的设计&lt;/