U6CXDE0WN38FzbxrqRQ30Qo-geLTQE8mxu0XE4Vnoq0nHLIPSbvW5th3NeGJkRxBeo8iFTGT9cbfVHimxXtrsts1HGQFL2Lv4_dikaOzyyPA-WE2Sa5hHhh0s7NxAix8fijep-OoA07uXvHw/qgo9AgegUEShrp98GYOmPZnJQvZpFFC6/18" target="_blank"&gt;下调了总统的关税&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;联邦上诉法院裁定特朗普的举动非法，6比3的多数票——其中包括特朗普自己挑选的两名候选人（特朗普&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/mmor5yZ6xZIwIlq3kShOnINMLkJYDa5fLU6QFyiIWN596XTM2ZXBRVjs1AxeXefSF9wSJlZF94GbAzeHmaiyzC5jZ-wxxFV5WKodIjtqh3GplZ0TksfAGn6nmW2BeEhxtAIysWl08r0s8a0f8ErNaDhiaUc99NM-ML88VIBvQjppkok_RA6T7SW5uQcXO2VwwM9lBkZ0eGiib2B7e1FbDku__dN0BUPd6ViYlcDonWBItYUysJBW7OH3Hm-XvtHZaUZkTp1Nx7X2QEhIzHEq-L3dMS8P-sM22jHePw6PglK6OyHlunAKx3qe29QGULpINNC7JaZwKwKKLVRsj3VUcj6Yd5zqs4d0xePmH3lCf_xWfRZTHag9vLEKsg/BmgkKKvJUVjq_ZWeSX38QKxeIDwFJ9_L/18" target="_blank"&gt;以非常个人化的方式攻击了&lt;/a&gt;他们）——确认了联邦上诉法院的裁决，推翻了共和党标志性的经济政策。在随后的新闻发布会上，这位79岁的老人迅速发难。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;特朗普称一些法官是“耻辱”和“不忠诚”，同时还暗示了一些非具体的外国阴谋，用他的话说，这些阴谋是由“ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/lJIvR_1Wu1xlAGDWEYRHyFtUtOwYrj2xAE930NlD5yTiOcH1QTb3DBXzW4CmrdFLWGRGgj3JFpM1jxTCZUCx6cLQ-64lUo2Fl2anrwpRHmcBGhmD8aS-VwtP8zq6kv6vu5vEZGkqvTt0wG2B-QzRa9jYFkCCFFMPMCJ1Sr4byBy3NPAd3YkJUarf3fUHPYTdBCRgyIoyqYoAJ0ZewtnPd98ncERFGt3aiHHV254TlOhfYVty_ctyYN7wg5XBCTecnAFsnSKINDy2bOPIvRDf_JuhJwOq02k-k8xG1H1HTqR9W7c95quAPUyJc9wAOqlWGwtiY0QteZn5WC8v6shQU7K07zIfrp-gUEsbFCxPcRDM0dulUWQ75K1umQ/MPp-unaj-IDl7AQ6FDSbW6gQ3NiJQ-ex/18" target="_blank"&gt;粘液球&lt;/a&gt;”意图影响法院而策划的。这次具有里程碑意义的失败发生之际，特朗普的支持率因他对经济的处理和他的国家移民拉网而不断下降。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;但是，尽管总统对不按自己的意愿表现出异常的愤怒，但政府一直在为失败做好准备，并计划&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/y0RZzYwZq8UObKhPFuKDhRjprbLqbf1daJfsqMHwthQPpdof-rE19bwAimYbIB84nwa-o2yN9l542Gs1XHaYCQiBvrAemWMjbb6yRjBIsgk8IGjwM3tflwl-pXx4eGrtJbaTC1NeK4BkI-6LaZpcFgneBdRzo94ZPRfr6pDk-NMm0y-XeZkWHy3xrwfS3NMAi196Xu-ObfxxcH0c2yhXsZUIYzwnYe-GbmeI9Ma-u4qo1O0UnzXUHODs